text: Md. Yunus Khan is a Bangladesh Nationalist Party politician and the former Member of Parliament of Barisal-6. ==Career== Khan was elected to parliament from Barisal-6 as a Bangladesh Nationalist Party candidate in 1991. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:5th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing Category:1994 deaths
title: Md. Yunus Khan
